jiraissue.summary: Review logic update announcement status and equipment status of PIS.
jiraissue.description: Hi Sa,As SRS common, if driver receive invalid data of message, driver will discard invalid data and continue to process remaining valid data.PIS driver checked structure of message when received by XML schema+ if message is invalid, raise malformed data on step parse message and end of the flow.+ otherwise, driver invokes according handlers.So message is valid structure when driver invokes handlers, hence Validate handlers is not necessary because it take responsibility to detect invalid data and remove invalid part out of message. That will impact to performance of driver.Validation should be execute on process handlers. If driver detect invalid data, it will discard invalid part and continue process.Please check and consider my comment.
